description:
Factory balls, a Bart Bonte game.
The objective of the game is to change the shape and color of a white ball and match a picture pasted on the side of the open box, by using the ball with a set of different tools provided.

Can you produce the ball on the box in each of the 44 levels?
Drag and drop the ball over the tools or just tap the tools.

The game supports all Android screen sizes: phones and tablets.

